msgid ""
"The installed version of at least one of your modules or themes has "
"been revoked and is no longer available for download. Upgrading or "
"uninstalling is strongly recommended!"
msgstr ""
"La versión instalada de al menos uno de sus módulos o temas ha sido "
"revocada y ya no está disponible para su descarga. Se recomienda "
"encarecidamente actualizar o desinstalar."

