"Drupal core does not immediately delete temporary file. For webform "
"submissions it is recommended that temporary files are immediately "
"deleted."
msgstr ""
"El core de Drupal no elimina inmediatamente los archivos temporales. "
"Para los envíos de Webform, se recomienda que los archivos temporales "
"se eliminen de forma inmediata."

